OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775661069
OL,3,CDisruption expected as doctors begin
OL,4,Csix-day strike across the South West
OL,6,FResident doctors across the South West
OL,7,Fhave begun six days of strike action
OL,8,Fafter a long-running dispute over pay
OL,9,Fand jobs.
OL,11,FThe national strike has been called by
OL,12,Fthe British Medical Association (BMA),
OL,13,Fwith Health Secretary, Wes Streeting
OL,14,Fdescribing the move as "disappointing".
OL,16,FResident doctors - formerly known as
OL,17,Fjunior doctors - will remain on strike
OL,18,Funtil 7am on Monday 13 April.
OL,26,@vD@XOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775661069
OL,3,CDisruption expected as doctors begin
OL,4,Csix-day strike across the South West
OL,6,FResident doctors were on strike at
OL,7,FBristol Royal Infirmary on Tuesday
OL,8,Fmorning, with some drivers in passing
OL,9,Fvehicles honking their horns in
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FOne of those doctors, Dr Shivam
OL,13,FSharma, deputy chair of the BMA
OL,14,Fresident doctors committee said: "We
OL,15,Fare here today because doctors have a
OL,16,Fvision, where patients are seen within
OL,17,Ffour hours in A&E, where those
OL,18,Fpatients are able to get GP
OL,19,Fappointments, where staff are not
OL,20,Fburnt-out, it's not working out, staff
OL,21,Fare leaving, we are understaffed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775661069
OL,3,CDisruption expected as doctors begin
OL,4,Csix-day strike across the South West
OL,6,F"We want a proper workforce plan,
OL,7,Fproper investment in the NHS so we can
OL,8,Fhave a world-class system which works
OL,9,Ffor all.
OL,11,F"Striking means that we can start that
OL,12,Fconversation, these are political
OL,13,Fchoices, to underfund and understaff
OL,14,Fthe NHS. The Government has left us
OL,15,Fwith no choice."
OL,17,FWhich hospitals will be most impacted
OL,18,Fby the walk out?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
